<td tEditID="c1r1" style=" background-color:#FFFFFF; bEditID:r3st1; color:#000000; bLabel:main; font-size:12pt; font-family:arial;" aEditID="c1r1" locked="0" >
<![CDATA[<p class="MsoNormal" style=""><font face="Arial, sans-serif">Hi {!Contact.FirstName},<br></font><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;"><br>I am getting in touch as </span><b style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;">your policy will expire in the next couple of days</b><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;"> and we have been trying to reach you to discuss the renewal. It looks like </span><b style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;">we may not have the correct contact details for you</b><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;">.<br></span><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;"><br>If you would like to renew your insurance, we can do so over the phone in a matter of minutes.<br></span><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;"><br><i>(Remove for Admiral renewals)&nbsp;</i></span><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;">As specialists in business insurance for contractors and freelancers, we offer a price promise. We will beat any like for like quote*. For full details and terms and conditions*, please </span><a href="https://www.kingsbridge.co.uk/price-promise/" style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;">click here</a><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;">.<br></span><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;"><br>Please let me know a good time to call and the best number to reach you on. Alternatively, you can contact us on </span><b style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;">01242 808740</b><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;">.<br></span><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;"><br>Kind regards,<br></span><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;"><br>{!User.FirstName}&nbsp;<br></span><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;">Sales Team<br></span><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;"><br>E: salesteam@kingsbridge.co.uk<br></span><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;">T: 01242 808740</span></p><p class="MsoNormal" style=""><br></p>]]></td>
</tr>
</table>